\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECraft File:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/dakfua1bq1dr0hx/TR-2L%20Light%20Craft.zip?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/dakfua1bq1dr0hx/TR-2L%20Light%20Craft.zip?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EPart 2: Draining of Fuel Showing Transition from Wheels Contacting the Surface to Floating Above the Surface.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVideo Evidence:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWeight changing in real time showing wheels raising off the surface\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/gxATNaLGGys\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/gxATNaLGGys\u003C/a\u003E (24 Seconds)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESteps to Replicate:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoad 0120FuelDrainKSC\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nBecause the rover is moving on loading use physics warp to speed up the process if desired.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESave File:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/m8wwwzy9zec03yp/0120FuelDrainKSC.zip?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/m8wwwzy9zec03yp/0120FuelDrainKSC.zip?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECraft File:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/jqp1qpbrg421pjg/TR-2L%20Viable%20Mass%20Tester.zip?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/jqp1qpbrg421pjg/TR-2L%20Viable%20Mass%20Tester.zip?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAdditional Information:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe approximate weight that a rover needs to be is 1.93t or over for the wheels to look like they are working naturally. Here is a picture of the craft file from Part 2:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022image.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1039965578754007060/1110373771874943016/image.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-11T08:11:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis one might be fixed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-09-12T12:08:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah. This is fixed. Moving to the archive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}